*mpg321-0.2.10-r2 (17 Jul 2003)

  17 Jul 2003; Nick Hadaway <raker@gentoo.org> mpg321-0.2.10-r2.ebuild:
  Changed mad depend to media-libs/{libmad,libid3tag}

*mpg321-0.2.10-r1 (27 May 2002)

  14 Jan 2003; Jon Nall <nall@gentoo.org> mpg321-0.2.10-r1.ebuild :
  added ~ppc

  27 May 2002; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> mpg321-0.2.10-r1.ebuild
  files/digest-mpg321-0.2.10-r1.ebuild :

  The mpg123->mpg321 symlink is now only created if mpg123 doesn't own that
  file.  This is done using the configure option, by the way.  Thanks to
  Rachel Holmes for pointing that out.

*mpg321-0.2.10 (30 Mar 2002)
  30 Mar 2002; Spider <spider@gentoo.org>
  Same procedure as last time

*mpg321-0.2.9 (16 Mar 2002)

  16 Mar 2002; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> mpg321-0.2.9.ebuild :

  Version upgrade, by copying the old ebuild to a new name.

*mpg321-0.2.3 (1 Feb 2002)

  1 Feb 2002; G.Bevin <gbevin@gentoo.org> ChangeLog :
  
  Added initial ChangeLog which should be updated whenever the package is
  updated in any way. This changelog is targetted to users. This means that the
  comments should well explained and written in clean English. The details about
  writing correct changelogs are explained in the skel.ChangeLog file which you
  can find in the root directory of the portage repository.
